# Main loop

```javascript
function tickFrame() {
  updatePhysics();

  if (tick % 3 === 0) {
    spawnParticle();
  }

  updateParticles();
  updateCamera();
  tick++;
}

setInterval(tickFrame, 16);
```

This means roughly **60 FPS**.

